  "time_ut": 1658210756,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "LGBT \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0da0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dab\u0dba \u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dca\u0db4\u0dd6\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dab\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dad\u0dc4\u0db1\u0db8\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dda",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "LGBT propaganda is completely banned in Russia",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A new law in Russia has permanently banned the promotion of LGBT relationships in the country, labeling the propagation or promotion of such messages as war propaganda and incitement to hatred.",
        "Previously, LGBT advertising was banned in Russia, only when it was directed at children. But some politicians in the country have presented this bill as a result of demanding strict restrictions and punishments for \"rejection of family values\" and \"propagation of non-traditional sexual relations\".",
        "An explanatory note attached to the bill has indicated that LGBT propaganda has expanded in Russia. Accordingly, it has been shown that such relationships are promoted through the portrayal of such relationships in the country's media, public events, streaming services and films."
      ],
